OPEN SKIES CONFERENCE REMISSION ORDER - which provides for the remission of
customs and excise duties and sales and excise taxes paid or payable on
alcoholic beverages imported or purchased in Canada by official delegates
to the Open Skies Conference which was held in Ottawa.
